{"tid":243425,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴黎拍賣「愛情鎖」籌逾200萬助難民　示威者轟不應助「非法入境者」","createTime":"2017-05-14T15:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T15:48:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b81d3ae2fc9e9625f3470dc1a1eaa6444c480293","tid":243425,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"(20:39) - 20170514 - 國際<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/14/234101_90d28aaf8ee2f0193b4d11f12329a5ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F14%2F234101_90d28aaf8ee2f0193b4d11f12329a5ab.jpg&h=a91087b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國巴黎周六（13日）舉行慈善拍賣會，拍賣掛在巴黎各橋樑上的「愛情鎖」，共籌得約25萬歐元（約210.6萬港元）善款，將用於協助難民。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他報道：韶關夫婦憑DNA比對尋回35年被拐親女　母女相擁而哭　父：爸媽找你找得好苦啊！<br />\n<br />\n遊客常把「愛情鎖」扣在巴黎橋樑欄杆上，再將鑰匙丟進河中，象徵永不分離，其中最知名的是鄰近羅浮宮的「藝術橋」（Pont des Arts）。由於數以千計的鎖頭導致「藝術橋」部分塌陷，2015年起，巴黎政府禁止掛鎖，並着手拆除，部分舊鎖轉交巴黎市立典當行（Credit Municipal de Paris）拍賣。<br />\n<br />\n今次拍賣的共有150組鎖頭，它們與木材、行人路上的石塊或膠架組合成藝術品，另有來自藝術橋的15段欄杆出售，吸引數百人競投。大部分鎖頭藝術品都以每件150至200歐元（約1277至1703港元）成交，成交價最高的為「藝術橋」一段，重達470公斤的欄杆，以1.7萬歐元（約14.5萬港元）成交。有參與競投遊客期望，可將「巴黎的碎片」帶回家。<br />\n<br />\n拍賣共籌得約25萬歐元，將捐贈予3個協助安頓湧入巴黎難民的慈善組織。拍賣舉行期間，法國極右青年組織Generation Identitaire成員衝入會場，要求拍賣所得應歸予巴黎人，而不是「非法入境者」。示威者被驅逐離場。<br />\n<br />\n（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170514/s00005/1494766502620\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170514%2Fs00005%2F1494766502620&d=sOSR1epLEapJbLCvIyWedTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=22dc10cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170514%2Fs00005%2F1494766502620&h=93268c34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170514/s00005/1494766502620</a>"},{"pid":"29bf44de8e0e5901393b5f8d9153113410bab0ed","tid":243425,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"呢個國家冇撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地黎你國家打家劫舍樣樣齊，個國家d人民就日日大愛撚上身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe8b2cc11a603eedf4a917ef3097c3c0b5c82c7","tid":243425,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"法國人真係好識markup嚟呃錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1305e9c33072f410f49f141c201e57d59c1c655a","tid":243425,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}